  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO REQUIRE THE DEPARTMENT OF ENVIRONMENTAL QUALITY TO APPROVE OR DENY PERMITS WITHIN A PRESCRIBED TIME FRAME, AND IF IT FAILS TO DO SO, DEEM THE PERMIT APPROVED TO BRING FORWARD SECTIONS 49-27-9, 49-27-23, 49-27-37, 51-3-5 AND 53-7-39, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, WHICH RELATE TO CERTAIN PERMITS, FOR PURPOSE OF POSSIBLE AMENDMENT; TO AMEND SECTIONS 49-17-29, 49-17-34 AND 49-27-11, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO MAKE MINOR, NONSUBSTANTIVE CHANGES; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
